title: David Bowie  - Wish Upon A Star
description:
Another very nice David Bowie bootleg. Check my account for more Bowie stuff.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)


David Bowie - Wish Upon A Star (1976) Flac [1cd]
The Inglewood Forum
Los Angeles, CA, USA
9th February 1976
Excellent Audience Recording
Artwork Included

Lineage: SilverCD--> EAC(secure)--> Flac(level.8)--> you

[quote]The L.A. songs are recorded off the vinyl with the same title, 
and the excellent sound quality is maintained. The songs marked * are from the Rotterdam show, 
and for the first time is PANIC IN DETROIT from that show available on disc. 
The Rotterdam songs are sound-board recordings just like the previously available songs from the same concert. 
The only unreleased song from that show now is QUEEN BITCH. Very nice "filler bits"! 
The CD is said to be Japanese, but it is Italian. Anyway, a disc I warmly recommend! -BASSMAN[/quote]
